actions.text: Referred to House Committee on Rules.
Committee Consideration and Mark-up Session Held.
Reported to House by House Committee on Rules. Report No: 98-1.
Called up by House by Unanimous Consent.
Resolution Agreed to in House by Yea-Nay Vote: 312 - 69 (Record Vote No: 6).

official_title: A resolution to establish the Select Committee on Children, Youth, and Families.

summary.text: Establishes in the House of Representatives the Select Committee on Children, Youth, and Families to conduct a comprehensive study and review of the problems of children, youth, and families.

titles.title: A resolution to establish the Select Committee on Children, Youth, and Families.
